Command:
    new-exp             : Create new experiment folder from template.
        Essentially extracts the base experiment structure from the experiment_template.zip.
        After doing that, you should follow the instructions found in "New experiment" section
        in the base README of the project to make sure the new experiment is functional.

Arguments:
    exp [Required] : Name of the new experiment being created. Only letters and underscores as it
                     is partly a python module.

Examples:
    Create a new experiment called "goodbye_world"
        make new-exp exp=goodbye_world
